This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-bunch-linux layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Manual Installation
===================

  I. Adding the meta-bunch-linux layer to your build using repo tool
 II. Add meta-bunch-linux layer to bblayer
III. Use setup-environment script to configure the environment

II. Misc
========

